<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>intro-&gt;[introprefix], [introsuffix] 在 [place_name]、[place_adjective] 定居點和 [place_summary]，倖存者找到了脆弱的立足點。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>introprefix-&gt;炸彈落下、舊世界崩潰之後</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>危機(uses=2)-&gt;飢餓席捲了他們的定居點，迫使他們絕望地越過已知的邊界進行搜尋。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>危機(uses=2)-&gt;輻射風暴席捲大地，毒害地球和心靈，考驗著他們的決心。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>危機(uses=2)-&gt;變異的野獸和扭曲的恐怖物潛伏在黑暗中，威脅著每一步。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>危機(uses=2)-&gt;隨著倖存者中恐懼和懷疑的增長，內部衝突撕裂了他們的團結。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>危機(uses=2)-&gt;舊戰爭的幽靈在廢墟城市中迴盪，敵對派系爭奪以[place_powerCenter]為中心的搖搖欲墜的權力。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>危機(uses=2)-&gt;由輻射和污穢產生的荒地疾病席捲了整個社區，奪走了年輕人和老年人的生命，而且看不到治癒的方法。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>危機(uses=2)-&gt;不穩定的水源乾涸或中毒，迫使人們冒險前往遙遠、未知的綠洲。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>危機(uses=2)-&gt;天空被火山灰和風暴燃燒，遮蔽了陽光，讓大地寒冷刺骨。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>危機(uses=2)-&gt;敵對戰幫發動了殘酷的攻擊，夷平了農場和村莊，驅散了家庭，粉碎了脆弱的聯盟。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>危機(uses=2)-&gt;舊世界的技術搖搖欲墜和崩潰，倖存者不得不從廢品中拼湊出武器和工具，往往冒著巨大的風險。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>introprefix-&gt;核火災之後</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>危機(uses=2)-&gt;潛伏的非自然威脅的低語——被科學扭曲的變種人變得瘋狂——在人們中傳播恐懼和偏執。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>回應-&gt;[responseprefix]，[responsesuffix] 在 [place_community] 這樣的中心周圍，[place_adjective] 人民團結起來，其中包括維持脆弱和平的 [place_job]。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>responseprefix-&gt;有些人轉向了舊方法</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>響應前綴-&gt;領導者玫瑰 - 軍閥</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>responseprefix-&gt;他們與鄰近團體建立了脆弱的聯盟</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>響應前綴-&gt;其他人擁抱無情的生存主義</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>responseprefix-&gt;宗教邪教和奇怪的新信仰蓬勃發展</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>responseprefix-&gt;熟練的拾荒者和工程師重新利用舊技術</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>響應後綴-&gt;接受部落儀式和祖先精神的指導。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>回應後綴 -&gt; 選舉產生的議會 - 每個議會都聲稱對其人民具有權威。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>introprefix-&gt;第一次世界大戰留下的傷痕比沙漠和廢墟更深</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>回應後綴-&gt;交易知識、武器和希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>響應後綴-&gt;先發制人，對敵人毫不留情。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>回應後綴-&gt;在混亂中提供意義。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>響應後綴-&gt;保衛和維持他們的家園。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>改造-&gt;[transformationprefix], [transformationsuffix] 他們的大廳，就像[place_powerCenter]一樣，成為混亂中秩序的象徵。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>conversionprefix-&gt;隨著時間的推移，他們的習俗變成了法律</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>轉型前綴-&gt;最初分散的倖存者成長為一股強大的力量</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>轉型前綴-&gt;他們的旗幟在戰場和議會大廳中升起</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>改造字首-&gt;一些定居古城遺址</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>轉型前綴-&gt;苦難的傷痕烙印在他們身上</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>introprefix-&gt;當文明衰退時</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>轉型前綴-&gt;傳奇圍繞他們的領導者成長</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>轉變後綴-&gt;儀式，以及牢不可破的誓言。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>轉化後綴-&gt;在整個廢土中令人恐懼和尊重。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>變換後綴-&gt;團結和力量的象徵。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>轉變後綴-&gt;將腐爛變成希望的堡壘。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>轉變後綴-&gt;打造一個永遠不會向牆外的恐怖低頭的民族。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>轉變後綴-&gt;火光講述的故事，激勵後代。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>遺產-&gt;[legacyprefix]，[legacysuffix]曾經只是[place_name]的一群倖存者，現在他們成為了堅韌的證明。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>遺留前綴-&gt;現在</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>遺產前綴-&gt;從破碎的開始</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>introsuffix-&gt;分散的倖存者在受輻射的廢墟中求生。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>Legacyprefix-&gt;他們的故事是關於韌性的故事</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>LegacyPrefix-&gt;雖然廢物很嚴苛</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>LegacyPrefix-&gt;隨著舊世界的消逝</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>LegacyPrefix-&gt;時間會評斷他們</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>遺產後綴-&gt;他們的名字在荒原上迴響，是盟友的燈塔，也是對敵人的警告。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>遺產後綴-&gt;他們在新世界中佔有一席之地，從灰燼中塑造未來。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>遺產後綴-&gt;證明在廢墟中團結的力量。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>遺產後綴-&gt;他們的遺產永垂不朽－銘刻在石頭上，在風中低語。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>遺產後綴-&gt;他們的新秩序崛起，這是野蠻土地上脆弱的希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>遺產字尾-&gt;他們是救世主還是怪物－但他們的影響是不可否認的。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>introsuffix-&gt;灰燼誕生了新的部落、幫派和為生存而奮鬥的定居點。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>introsuffix-&gt;從這些傷痕中崛起了羽翼未豐的社區。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>introsuffix-&gt;絕望的人和充滿希望的人聚集在破碎的天空下閃爍的營火周圍。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>危機(uses=2)-&gt;他們與[place_foeLeader]領導的野蠻襲擊者作戰，指揮著殘酷的[place_foeSoldiers]。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>
</LanguageData>
